name: Snapper fwish gets trapped!
description:
Fun facts about Snapper:
- Snappers can grow to about 40 inches, weigh up to 50 pounds and live more than 50 years.
- Generally, Snappers live in schools of approximately the same size, larger Snappers are generally loners.
- Snappers are carnivorous fish and feed on sea worms and small crustaceans found in the ocean.
